@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About GreenGo";
}

<style>
    /* Base Styles */
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        background-color: #fafafa;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    p {
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero-banner {
        position: relative;
        height: 450px;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        animation: fadeSlideIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    .hero-overlay h1 {
        font-size: 2.8em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-overlay p {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    /* About Section */
    .about-section {
        padding: 70px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        background: #ffffff;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .about-section:hover {
        background: #f7fdf3;
    }

    .about-content {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
    }

    .what-is-greengo h2 {
        font-size: 2.2em;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        color: #507d2a;
    }

    .what-is-greengo p {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .greengo-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 30px auto;
        max-width: 650px;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .greengo-list li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        padding-left: 35px;
        position: relative;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .greengo-list li:before {
        content: '🌱';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: -2px;
        font-size: 1.4em;
    }

    .greengo-list li:hover {
        transform: translateX(8px);
        color: #6fa524;
    }

    /* Promise Section */
    .promise-section {
        background: #f5f9ef;
        padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .promise-section h2 {
        font-size: 2.2em;
        color: #4a5d3a;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .promise-cards {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 40px;
    }

    .promise-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        padding: 25px;
        width: 280px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .promise-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .promise-card .icon {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .promise-card .icon img {
        width: 75px;
        height: 75px;
        object-fit: contain;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .promise-card:hover .icon img {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .promise-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.3em;
        color: #4a5d3a;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .promise-card p {
        font-size: 1em;
        color: #555;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
        background-color: #4a5d3a;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 0.95em;
        margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .footer p {
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @@keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; }
        to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @@keyframes fadeSlideIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-banner {
            height: 320px;
        }

        .hero-overlay h1 {
            font-size: 1.9em;
        }

        .hero-overlay p {
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .promise-card {
            width: 90%;
        }

        .what-is-greengo h2,
        .promise-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 480px) {
        .hero-overlay h1 {
            font-size: 1.6em;
        }

        .greengo-list {
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="hero-banner" style="background-image: url('@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/about.jpg")');">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
        <h1>Looking for Green Escapes?</h1>
        <p>Discover, book, and enjoy nature-inspired destinations — right here in NCR.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="about-section what-is-greengo">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>What is GreenGo?</h2>
        <p><strong>GreenGo is your gateway to exploring eco-friendly destinations across Metro Manila.</strong></p>
        <p>
            Whether you’re looking for a peaceful park stroll, an educational museum visit, or a refreshing nature retreat,
            <strong>GreenGo NCR</strong> helps you find sustainable experiences that bring you closer to nature — responsibly.
            We make discovering, booking, and organizing green escapes easier than ever.
        </p>

        <ul class="greengo-list">
            <li>Discover eco-parks, museums, and sustainable travel activities.</li>
            <li>Book guided tours and reserve slots online in just a few taps.</li>
            <li>Manage payments and reservations seamlessly in one hub.</li>
            <li>Save and revisit your favorite green destinations anytime.</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="font-weight:600; font-size:1.1em; color:#4a5d3a;">
            Traveling green has never been this rewarding — or this simple.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="about-section promise-section">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>What We Promise</h2>
        <div class="promise-cards">
            <div class="promise-card">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="~/Content/Images/simplicity.png" alt="Simplicity">
                </div>
                <h3>Simplicity</h3>
                <p>
                    From discovering to booking, GreenGo ensures a smooth, intuitive experience for every eco-traveler.
                    No clutter, no confusion — just effortless exploration.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="promise-card">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="~/Content/Images/authenticity.png" alt="Authenticity">
                </div>
                <h3>Authenticity</h3>
                <p>
                    Each destination we feature reflects genuine sustainability.
                    GreenGo highlights real places that care for the planet, not just green aesthetics.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="promise-card">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="~/Content/Images/discovery.png" alt="Discovery">
                </div>
                <h3>Discovery</h3>
                <p>
                    We continually seek new eco-locations across NCR — hidden gardens, quiet riversides,
                    and inspiring cultural spots — for you to experience next.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


